How to setup SRT 

Create a duplicate or new profile if necessary so it does not disrupt your personal settings.   
![][image1]

Preferred settings is *720p 30fps or 1080p 30fps* and make sure bitrate is not higher than 4500

Create a new scene if necessary

Mute the default audio sources in the Audio Mixer \> **Desktop Audio** and **Mic/Aux**  
**![][image2]**

Create a new source **Game Capture![][image3]**

You may need to full screen the source *right click \>*  *transform \> fit screen*

Create an audio source **Audio Application Capture**  
**![][image4]**
